- cs.SD (Software Development) is another possible category as the paper discusses the development of microservices-based systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the use of specific microservice architecture patterns. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper shares a dataset of microservice-based projects.
